thread.title: Manhattan Rents Fell 2.7% in December to Median of $3,295

author: Josh Barbanel
title: Manhattan Rents Fell 2.7% in December to Median of $3,295
text:

The median Manhattan monthly rent was $3,295 in December, down 2.7% from a record December rent of $3,388 last year, according to a report being released Thursday by Douglas Elliman real estate. It was the biggest year-over-year monthly decline...
